/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b8366498479f5ce3401c79b95862e570a078a2","tid":414404,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連落街跑步做gym都會帶身份證<br />\n比差佬查都唔洗比人的返去差館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係落一落街都會帶，但有啲客唔帶仲要串柒柒咁指住個鼻話我唔識佢，我好想call差佬嚟查佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eca1c0dee106a1ddea04359aadae19e17b5eda","tid":414404,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你想做邊間呀？<br />\n我次次都好快咋，好似幾日就有消息</blockquote><br />\n恒生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我曾經apply過，佢好似有send email打嚟叫我填野，又打過嚟但我miss咗call,不過印象中恆生係等等耐啲，中小銀行就快好多。</blockquote><br />\n有冇邊啲會快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該晒吉妹</blockquote><br />\n交通第二日就打嚟，出得起錢但好辛苦的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁快！我等左好耐啦，我今晚試下交通先，吉妹有冇邊間推薦？</blockquote><br />\n你本身有無做緊/做過？</blockquote><br />\n冇啊 冇經驗"}]}